## **2. Hospital Database (with Constraints)**

```sql
CREATE TABLE Patients (
    pnum NUMBER,
    pname VARCHAR2(20) NOT NULL,
    age NUMBER CHECK (age > 0),
    CONSTRAINT pk_patients PRIMARY KEY (pnum)
);
```

```sql
CREATE TABLE Doctors (
    dnum NUMBER,
    dname VARCHAR2(20) NOT NULL,
    phono NUMBER UNIQUE,
    rank VARCHAR2(20),
    CONSTRAINT pk_doctors PRIMARY KEY (dnum)
);
```

```sql
CREATE TABLE Visits (
    pnum NUMBER,
    dnum NUMBER,
    vdate DATE,
    diagnosis VARCHAR2(30),
    CONSTRAINT pk_visits PRIMARY KEY (pnum, dnum),
    CONSTRAINT fk_vis_pat FOREIGN KEY (pnum) REFERENCES Patients(pnum),
    CONSTRAINT fk_vis_doc FOREIGN KEY (dnum) REFERENCES Doctors(dnum)
);
```

