## **4. Supplier–Parts Database (with Constraints)**

```sql
CREATE TABLE Suppliers (
    sid NUMBER,
    sname VARCHAR2(20) NOT NULL,
    address VARCHAR2(30),
    CONSTRAINT pk_suppliers PRIMARY KEY (sid)
);
```

```sql
CREATE TABLE Parts (
    pid NUMBER,
    pname VARCHAR2(20) NOT NULL,
    color VARCHAR2(10),
    CONSTRAINT pk_parts PRIMARY KEY (pid)
);
```

```sql
CREATE TABLE Catalog (
    sid NUMBER,
    pid NUMBER,
    cost NUMBER(8,2) CHECK (cost > 0),
    CONSTRAINT pk_catalog PRIMARY KEY (sid, pid),
    CONSTRAINT fk_cat_sup FOREIGN KEY (sid) REFERENCES Suppliers(sid),
    CONSTRAINT fk_cat_part FOREIGN KEY (pid) REFERENCES Parts(pid)
);
```

