## **5. Sailors Database (with Constraints)**

```sql
CREATE TABLE Sailors (
    sid NUMBER,
    sname VARCHAR2(20) NOT NULL,
    rating NUMBER CHECK (rating BETWEEN 1 AND 10),
    age NUMBER(4,1) CHECK (age > 0),
    CONSTRAINT pk_sailors PRIMARY KEY (sid)
);
```

```sql
CREATE TABLE Boats (
    bid NUMBER,
    bname VARCHAR2(20),
    color VARCHAR2(10),
    CONSTRAINT pk_boats PRIMARY KEY (bid)
);
```

```sql
CREATE TABLE Reserves (
    sid NUMBER,
    bid NUMBER,
    day DATE,
    CONSTRAINT pk_reserves PRIMARY KEY (sid, bid),
    CONSTRAINT fk_res_sail FOREIGN KEY (sid) REFERENCES Sailors(sid),
    CONSTRAINT fk_res_boat FOREIGN KEY (bid) REFERENCES Boats(bid)
);
```


